{"word":"G1103 - γνήσιος - gnḗsios - gnay'-see-os - Own","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γνήσιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">gnḗsios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">gnay'-see-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Own</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உண்மை, உத்தம - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"legitimately born, not spurious; genuine, true, sincere"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G1077 - γενέσια - genésia - ghen-es'-ee-ah/1077\">G1077</a>; <i>legitimate</i> (of birth), that is, <i>genuine:</i> - own, sincerity, true.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}